## Where to Place This in Pega

You have three options — pick whichever fits your app:
```
Option A:  Harness (best — loads once per session)
           → pyCaseWorkerHarness or your custom harness
           → Add a Section with this HTML block
           → Loads when investigator logs in
           → Never reloads unless full page refresh

Option B:  Case Type Section (loads per case open)
           → Add to your main case wrapper section
           → The guard (if !window._caseTrackerInitialized)
             prevents duplicate initialization

Option C:  Portal Header / Footer
           → If you have a custom portal
           → Add as an HTML fragment
           → Loads once, persists across all navigation
